ness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15362,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/24\/seeing-muhammad-in-your-dreams\/","url_meta":{"origin":9762,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Visions: Seeing the Prophet in your dreams","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever sees me in a dream has truly seen me, for Satan cannot imitate me.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6994, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2266 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5952,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/06\/none-say-muhammad-better-yunus\/","url_meta":{"origin":9762,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Yunus: None should say Muhammad better than Jonah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo servant should say that I am better than Jonah son of Mata.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \"Whoever says that I am better than Jonah son of Mata has told a lie.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3234,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u